{
  "id": "adv_event_2108_01_05",
  "title": "芽衣の恋",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――IDOL beach Fes、月ストの出番直前",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Right before Moon Tempest’s show at IDOL beach Fes",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "endTime": 2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 2.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_05-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "お客さんの入り、いいみたいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I hear the attendance is good.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.333333333333333,
      "endTime": 7.069523700078328,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 7.266666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_05-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、元々人気のフェスですが\n今年は異例の観客動員数なんですって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ this is always a popular festival‚ and this year in particular\nis attracting a lot of people.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.266666666666667,
      "endTime": 13.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 13.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_05-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "いいねー、今夜は月も綺麗だし\n月ストにとって、きっと最高のステージになるよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nice. And the moon’s pretty tonight.\nThis is sure to be the greatest show for Moon Tempest!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.7,
      "endTime": 21.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_05-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "なってもらわないと困りますわ\n新曲作りにどれだけ苦労したか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It better be.\nWe put so much work into writing the new song…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.3,
      "endTime": 27.533333333333335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 27.733333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_05-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "そうだね、振り付けも歌合せも\n完成したの昨日だもんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sure did‚ and the choreography‚ and the lyrics.\nWe only finished it yesterday.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.733333333333334,
      "endTime": 33.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_05-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "こないだ沖縄で行われたイベントでは\nサニーピースが出演して大成功だったって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "At an event in Okinawa the other day‚\nSunny Peace performed and they were a huge success.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.4,
      "endTime": 39.84889714188046,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 40.06666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_05-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "さくら達には、絶対に負けられない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No way we can lose to Sakura and the others.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.06666666666667,
      "endTime": 43.03464852968852,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 43.233333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_05-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね。彼女達は大切な仲間ですけど\n一番のライバルでもありますから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re right. They’re important fellow idols for us‚\nbut they’re also our biggest rivals.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.233333333333334,
      "endTime": 49.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_05-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫だよ！　私達はサニーピースみたいに\nザ・夏！　ってグループじゃないけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s fine! It’s not like we’re the\ngroup that screams “Summer” like Sunny Peace.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50,
      "endTime": 57.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 57.266666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_05-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "今回の新曲は、私達、月のテンペストらしい夏を\n歌ってるもん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Our new song will be about a “Moon Tempest Summer‚”\ndone in our own way!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.266666666666666,
      "endTime": 62.93333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_05-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "夜空じゃなきゃ、花火も月も綺麗に見えないよ\n太陽みたいに眩しくはないけど――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If it’s not night‚ we won’t be able to see the fireworks or the moon clearly.\nThey’re not as glaringly bright as the sun‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.13333333333333,
      "endTime": 70.66666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 70.86666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_05-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "だからこそ綺麗な光があるんだと思うの\n私達は、そんなグループでいようよ。これからも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but that’s what makes them shine so beautifully.\nLet’s be that kind of group‚ from now on.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.86666666666666,
      "endTime": 79.70000000000002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_05-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.9,
      "endTime": 82.10000000000001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_05-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣ちゃん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei-chan…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.3,
      "endTime": 84.33333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 84.53333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_05-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "え？　何、何？　どうしたの、みんな\n芽衣、おかしなこと言っちゃった？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? What? What happened‚ all of you?\nDid I say something strange?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.53333333333333,
      "endTime": 90.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 91.13333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_05-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "ううん、逆だよ、芽衣ちゃん\nとっても素敵だったよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ Mei-chan. Just the opposite.\nThat was wonderful!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.13333333333334,
      "endTime": 96.66666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 96.86666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_05-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "そうですわ！　あの芽衣が\nこんなに立派なことを言うなんて……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It really was. Our Mei of all‚\nsaying something so magnificent!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.86666666666666,
      "endTime": 103.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 103.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_05-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "私、すごーく、すごーーく感動しましたわ！\n頭を撫でて差し上げます！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m so‚ so‚ totally moved!\nI’ll pat you on the head!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.3,
      "endTime": 111.23333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 111.43333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_05-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "あはは、すずにゃん、くすぐったいよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahaha. Suzu-nyan‚ that tickles.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.43333333333334,
      "endTime": 115.55872915585836,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 115.76666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_05-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、仲良しですね\n……あっ、そろそろ時間です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe‚ you’re such good friends.\n…Oh‚ it’s almost time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.76666666666667,
      "endTime": 120.50000000000001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_05-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "行こう、みんな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let’s go‚ everyone!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.7,
      "endTime": 122.53333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 122.76666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_05-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "あの日みんなで見た花火みたいに\n綺麗に輝こうね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let’s sparkle beautifully‚ like the fireworks\nwe saw together that day!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.76666666666667,
      "endTime": 127.56666666666668,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6066.666666666677
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfesstage-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfesstage-00-night",
      "startTime": 128.83333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_05-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう！　みんな大好き――っ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you! I love you all!",
